{"tid":899174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄒文懷家祭　殯儀館拒收劉德華花圈","createTime":"2018-11-12T08:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T10:51:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3b5ca68a711def5602005986d4e423855b2a4db3","tid":899174,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181112/20543950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F20543950&d=qdWU1xkqc807tCKxwTAPSwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c70772b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F20543950&h=a8027fac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181112/20543950</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月12日 <br />\n<br />\n鄒文懷家祭　殯儀館拒收劉德華花圈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181112/large/12la5p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181112%2Flarge%2F12la5p7.jpg&h=4c76c588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄒文懷　1927－2018<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港影業大亨鄒文懷上月30日離世，享年91歲，其家人遵從其生前意願，喪禮一切低調，並由女兒鄒重珩全權負責。有消息指鄒家昨天於香港殯儀館進行家祭儀式，今日上午出殯，但喪禮不對外開放，也不接受傳媒採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n少數至親獲邀出席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181112/large/12la5p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181112%2Flarge%2F12la5p6.jpg&h=80dcc516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉德華致送的花圈（右）遭殯儀館拒收，司機將花圈運走。仇志德攝<br />\n<br />\n昨午大批記者在殯儀館等候，下午約4時許，分別有劉德華、映藝娛樂有限公司、盧永仁博士的花圈送來，但殯儀館拒絕接收。送花來的司機只好將花圈放在殯儀門外拍照作交代，然後將花圈運走。送花司機接受訪問說：「殯儀前台話唔需要送上去。」<br />\n<br />\n據知鄒文懷昨天的家祭不是在殯儀館舉行，而是在家中進行，而且只是至親可以獲邀出席，一個影視圈的朋友都沒有獲通知出席，連成龍數度聯絡鄒重珩也聯絡不上。不過今天的出殯儀式會安排在香港殯儀館舉行，但同樣只有少數至親可以獲邀出席。昨日由香港電影11大屬會組成的香港電影工作者總會向會員發出內部通告，指前嘉禾機構集團創辦人鄒文懷先生周前辭世，悉家族以私人喪禮儀式，同業友好未能作最後送別，總會謹此代表友好向鄒氏家族致深此哀悼。<br />\n<br />\n雖然家人保持低調，但鄒文懷把一生都貢獻給電影事業，又積極將香港電影推向國際，為香港電影工業貢獻良多，為不少電影同業所敬重。香港電影工作者總會昨日發放悼文紀念他，內容指業界對這位一代電影偉人的離世深感哀痛：「鄒文懷先生以無比魄力及獨到眼光，自上世紀70年代帶領香港電影在東南亞以至國際寫下精彩輝煌的一頁，令香港享有東方荷里活的美譽，鄒先生的貢獻功在當代，利在千秋！由於鄒先生的喪禮以私人儀式舉行，同業未能作最後送別，香港電影工作者總會暨十一大屬會代表所有會員謹此敬悼，並向鄒先生的家人致以最深切的慰問。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者卓寶花  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n重案組登記領隊資料　疑10團違規"},{"pid":"a56f5dafd4d74f9a612196ec9c9b4f0d2f0f851e","tid":899174,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"有仇?"},{"pid":"167f4baec3db6e90930db34b37924a9349aa02cf","tid":899174,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d19d65396c4995013afd8ae6fee7e24b59a075f","tid":899174,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a56f5dafd4d74f9a612196ec9c9b4f0d2f0f851e","tid":899174,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"有仇?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbfd93f52e958281ae2488cb610d6749971d7b7","tid":899174,"uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a56f5dafd4d74f9a612196ec9c9b4f0d2f0f851e","tid":899174,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"有仇?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"據知鄒文懷昨天的家祭不是在殯儀館舉行，而是在家中進行"},{"pid":"96d06e65383dd61d7b92d7cf4803609b9b8b9c30","tid":899174,"uid":65984,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a56f5dafd4d74f9a612196ec9c9b4f0d2f0f851e","tid":899174,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"有仇?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"我都諗過有日我死左, 唔好搞任何儀式<br />\n拎去火化左, 將D骨灰撒入大海<br />\n唔一定每個人都想風光大葬, 純粹係個人意願"},{"pid":"247e4fa78189d398008c36848d2c04f37960f756","tid":899174,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dbfd93f52e958281ae2488cb610d6749971d7b7","tid":899174,"uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a56f5dafd4d74f9a612196ec9c9b4f0d2f0f851e","tid":899174,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"有仇?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"據知鄒文懷昨天的家祭不是在殯儀館舉行，而是在家中進行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"成間屋都係花圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf7975999e810fa2badc452dd0c207b3ce485dd","tid":899174,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:31:14.000Z","msg":"連登毒撚一路都想咁低調<br />\n唔使做乜儀式<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcc63f30889ffd8383129144e873fb286570479","tid":899174,"uid":16676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:33:54.000Z","msg":"其實都好認同<br />\n花圈, 儀式<br />\n人亦遠去, 攪咁多做乜<br />\n簡簡單單就算<br />\n前塵往事, 不堪回首"},{"pid":"987c3689d592018d199e375a72eb41ca5cc4cfcd","tid":899174,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96d06e65383dd61d7b92d7cf4803609b9b8b9c30","tid":899174,"uid":65984,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a56f5dafd4d74f9a612196ec9c9b4f0d2f0f851e","tid":899174,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"有仇?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"我都諗過有日我死左, 唔好搞任何儀式<br />\n拎去火化左, 將D骨灰撒入大海<br />\n唔一定每個人都想風光大葬, 純粹係個人意願"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"58ddf30e740d4d5ad4df60c1d4093f40b4f85bde","tid":899174,"uid":164799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"講左唔招呼你<br />\n仲要黎<img src=\"/assets/